        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "Major Activities:1.1.1.      Inception Workshop with Local Governments1.1.2.      Formation and consultation meeting of Local Facilitation Committee for identification of beneficiaries.1.1.3.      Assessment of pre-identified potential schemes and Construction of selected most appropriate schemes in Cash for Work mechanism1.1.4.      Mobilization of Financial Service Provider for beneficiary registration and cash management.1.1.5.      Cash Disbursement to participants of Cash for Work1.1.6.      Distribution of Super Cereal Package to children of participants engaged in CFW.1.2.1 Consultation meetings with identified beneficiaries for identification of early recovery needs1.2.2 Selection and Orientation workshops for vendors supplying the livelihood inputs applying Voucher Modality1.2.3 Distribution of agriculture/livestock inputs to verified beneficiaries1.3.1. Consultation meetings with identified beneficiaries for identification of their business needs1.3.2. Conduction of business orientation for selected micro and small entrepreneurs1.3.3. (Business) Materials Support for selected micro and small entreprenueurs.1.3.4. Emergency Fund"
